reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Don't buy. Battery dead after just 6 months
reviews.reviewText: After just 6 months the battery will no longer charge. I only use it maybe 15 hrs a week at most. The company has offered a 40% discount off a new one which is a joke. I expect at least a one year warranty for most products being sold on Amazon. The Chinese company said it was Amazon's problem because it was fulfilled by them.Amazon are deliberately no help. You end up going round and round in circles and dead ends. Finally, I spoke to a CSR who could do nothing who then escalated to a supervisor. He was able to give me a return label and will refund BUT less restocking of $12.40. He said he was doing me a favoor and this was an exception. This is crazy. I surely am not the first person to buy a shoddy product from a Chinese company and want a refund within the one year warranty. If we all complained we could stop these crap Chinese companies selling bad products
